cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.EM, cs.AR, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the implementation of a neuromorphic network using metal oxide memristors, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The use of memristors also relates to the sub-category of electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET) and electromagnetism (cs.EM). The paper also mentions the classification task, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and possibly augmented reality (cs.AR).
